 of assisting students in continuing their education  Mr  Douglass has been at VMI since January 2015  Education Business Administration in Management   Organizational Leadership  George Fox University  Associate Degree in Air Traffic Control Management  Community College of The Air Force  Personal Mr  Douglass is married to Judy Douglass and they have 2 daughters  Morgan   Shannon  and a son  Sean  Mr  Douglass  passion is in volunteering and watching his children develop their talents in travel soccer  travel volleyball and recreation basketball  baseball and football ROTC Leadership Courses Info for Current Cadets Info for Prospective Cadets Army ROTC Awards Battalion Photo Gallery Army Links Faculty Mr  Thomas Atkinson Recruiting Operation Officer of Army ROTC P   540  464 7680 Main Office P   540  464 7351 F   540  464 7639 Virginia Military Institute 2020 Kilbourne Hall Lexington  VA  24450 Contact Army ROTC  ROTC Leadership Courses Info for Current Cadets Info for Prospective Cadets Army ROTC Awards Battalion Photo Gallery Army Links Faculty Mr  Thomas Atkinson Recruiting Operation Officer of Army ROTC P   540  464 7680 Main Office P   540  464 7351 F   540  464 7639 Virginia Military Institute 2020 Kilbourne Hall Lexington  VA  24450 Contact Army ROTC ROTC Leadership Courses Info for Current Cadets Info for Prospective Cadets Army ROTC Awards Battalion Photo Gallery Army Links Faculty ROTC Leadership ROTC Leadership Courses Courses Info for Current Cadets Info for Current Cadets Info for Prospective Cadets Info for Prospective Cadets Army ROTC Awards Army ROTC Awards Battalion Photo Gallery Battalion Photo Gallery Army Links Army Links Faculty Faculty Mr  Thomas Atkinson Recruiting Operation Officer of Army ROTC P   540  464 7680 Main Office P   540  464 7351 F   540  464 7639 Virginia Military Institute 2020 Kilbourne Hall Lexington  VA  24450 Contact Army ROTC Mr  Thomas Atkinson Recruiting Operation Officer of Army ROTC P   540  464 7680 Main Office P   5